HIV/AIDS: China ta ba da rahoton ƙaruwar kashi 14 cikin ɗari na masu kamuwa da cutar
A shekara ta 2010, an ba da rahoton cewa, yawan mutanen da suka kamu da cutar HIV da AIDS a China ya karu da kashi 14 cikin dari.
A kasar, fiye da mutane dubu 82 ne suka kamu da cutar, a cewar jami'an kiwon lafiya.
A cikin kwata na biyu na shekarar 2018 kawai, an bayar da rahoton kusan sabbin mutane 40,000.
Yawancin sabbin masu kamuwa da cutar suna kamuwa ne ta hanyar jima'i, kuma an ga canji a baya.
A China, HIV ya yadu cikin sauri a wasu yankuna sakamakon karɓar jinin da aka kamu da cutar.
Amma a wani taro a lardin Yunnan, jami'an lafiya na kasar Sin sun ce, wannan hanya ta rage yawan masu kamuwa da cutar HIV zuwa kusan babu.
Amma a China, adadin masu dauke da cutar HIV da AIDS ya karu da 100,000 a shekara guda.
A cikin al'ummar LGBT ta kasar Sin, kamuwa da cutar kanjamau ta hanyar jima'i babbar matsala ce.
A China, ko da yake an halatta luwadi a 1997, ana zargin cewa nuna wariya ga 'yan luwadi ya yi yawa.
Bincike ya nuna cewa, saboda ra'ayin mazan jiya na kasar, kimanin kashi 70 zuwa 90 cikin dari na maza masu luwadi ne za su auri mata.
Yawancin cututtuka suna faruwa ne a cikin irin wannan dangantaka idan ba a kiyaye ba.
Tun 2003 gwamnatin China ta yi alkawarin samar da maganin cutar HIV a ko'ina a kasar Sin a matsayin wani bangare na kokarin magance matsalar.
